<label>Thinking Budget ({{ editing.thinking_budget ?? 0 }})</label>
```

**脚本变更** — 替换 `alert()` 和 `confirm()`：

```typescript
// 之前：
alert('ID and Name are required')
confirm('Delete this agent?')
confirm('Reset to default agents? Custom agents will be lost.')

// 之后：
alert(t('agents.idNameRequired'))
confirm(t('agents.deleteConfirm'))
confirm(t('agents.resetConfirm'))
```

